##     the facets of a pure simplicial complex that you         ##
##     want to examine to a separate file                       ##
##                                                              ##
##        `BISTELLAR.testobject'                                ## 
##                                                              ##
##     or you can select a predefined complex:                  ##
##                                                              ##
